reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 3 inch binders fit and more
reviews.reviewText: My daughter loves this bag, she is a teen, her school doesn’t allow backpacks in classroom but her binders and books she needs for each class and her locker is too far away. She is allowed to carry this all day. She fits 2 3inch binders, a chrome book, some composition notebooks and more. There is a lot of space, the stitching is strong and holds up well. Ease to clean, great for the money. The bag is also soft and looks cute too! She has both the beige and slate grey kinda color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this one. I got the off white and the brown. Has a bit longer straps which is what I wanted, has an inside zipper pocket and outside pocket great for your phone. Very lightweight, soft material, casual but cute. Holds a lot. Had it for about 3 months now and holds up great, no visible wear and tear with regular use. HIGHLY recommend. Prob could be thrown in wash if needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I can’t think of a single con for this bag. It does everything a bag should do and can hold quite a lot! The texture is amazing and so soft, and it doesn’t seem to get dirty very easily. I like the neutral color as it fits with all outfits when going out and about. Not to mention the zipper is a huge plus! I don’t know about you but I’m not a fan of getting pickpocketed 😄

reviews.reviewText: Has a horrible smell so you’ll need to wash it before using it. Other than that is a pretty nice and spacious bag. I like it, might order another color!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Favorite tote bag!
reviews.reviewText: I had been in search of a spacious tote bag that actually had a zipper, and I’m so glad I came across this bag.It’s a great size, though personally I wouldn’t mind it being a tad bit bigger even. But it’s still a great size for daily use.I personally keep my purse in it- plus water bottles, a toiletry bag, a bag of snacks to take to work with me everyday and it’s perfect.The color is super cute and the material feels pretty good, like it will hold up for a while atleast. I’m grateful it doesn’t have one of those cheap zippers either, I’ve had no issues with it getting stuck like some bags like this do.HIGHLY recommend this bag. If you’re like me and like to carry a good amount of stuff around and want a casual cute bag this is perfect. Will definitely repurchase when this one eventually wears out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Brilliant material, plenty of space and pockets! Lovely colour and fantastic price.

I was looking for a cute tote bag to bring to school and work, and this is the perfect thing! It is able to hold my MacBook and some light books as well as my personal items. It also has a top zipper and some pockets within it so you can secure your items. The only downside of the bag is if you put too many heavy things in it it will make it painful to carry on your shoulder, so make sure not to overload it!
